summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Thirtieth Avenue South, from Judkins Street to the South line of All Around View Addition, et al, in the City of Seattle, by constructing concrete sidewalks under Ordinance No. 24362, creating Local Improvement District No. 2350 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
